<P><FONT SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ibm.com:
Online and telephone sales and assistance operations handle basic commodity transactions for large enterprises and small-to-medium businesses. </FONT></P>

