<P><FONT SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Global/major independent software vendors: ISVs deliver business process or industry-specific applications and, in doing so, often influence the sale of IBM
