systems integrators (SIs): SIs identify business problems and design solutions when Global Services is not the preferred systems integrator; they also sell computing
infrastructures from IBM and its competitors. </FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=2>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Regional
ISVs and SIs: SIs identify the business problems, and ISVs deliver business process or industry-specific applications to medium-sized and large businesses requiring IBM
